        <mxCell id="S-Zx8-YwdgRQVwYKoTbn-49" value="Things not included:&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Custom language creation wizard. Allow people to create their own languages and define their own rulesets. Give ability for people to request that their custom language become upstreamed and part of the standard set of langs.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A more sophisticated verb modification algorithm for irregular verbs. Exceptional verbs still follow certain rules sometimes, so when people modify an ending for one subject, maybe modify the endings automatically for the same subject across all tenses etc. Make the process of modifying irregular verb conjugations overall less painful.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="220" y="900" width="590" height="230" as="geometry" />
